@startuml

actor User

participant "Projet" as Projet
participant "Analyse" as Analyse
participant "Scanner Engine" as Scanner
participant "Semgrep" as Semgrep
participant "ESLint" as ESLint
participant "npmAudit" as NpmAudit
participant "Findings" as Findings
participant "PropositionCorrection" as Correction
participant "Rapport" as Rapport
database "BDD" as BDD


== Création du projet ==

User -> Projet: create()
activate Projet

Projet -> BDD: saveProject()
activate BDD
BDD --> Projet: project saved
deactivate BDD

Projet --> User: project created
deactivate Projet


== Lancement de l'analyse ==

User -> Analyse: start(projet)
activate Analyse

Analyse -> BDD: loadProject()
activate BDD
BDD --> Analyse: project loaded
deactivate BDD

Analyse -> Scanner: start scan
activate Scanner

Scanner -> Semgrep: scan code
Semgrep --> Scanner: results

Scanner -> ESLint: analyse JS
ESLint --> Scanner: results

Scanner -> NpmAudit: check dependencies
NpmAudit --> Scanner: vulnerabilities

Scanner -> Findings: generate findings
deactivate Scanner


== Stockage des résultats ==

activate Findings
Findings -> BDD: saveFindings()
activate BDD
BDD --> Findings: findings stored
deactivate BDD

Findings --> User: findings generated
deactivate Findings


== Proposition de correction ==

User -> Correction: request suggestions
activate Correction

Correction -> BDD: saveProposition()
activate BDD
BDD --> Correction: proposition saved
deactivate BDD

Correction --> User: suggestions available


User -> Correction: approve / reject
Correction -> BDD: updateStatus()
activate BDD
BDD --> Correction: status updated
deactivate BDD

Correction --> User: decision saved
deactivate Correction


== Génération du rapport ==

User -> Rapport: generate()
activate Rapport

Rapport -> BDD: loadFindings()
activate BDD
BDD --> Rapport: findings loaded
deactivate BDD

Rapport --> User: report generated


User -> Rapport: download()
Rapport --> User: report file

deactivate Rapport
deactivate Analyse

@enduml